          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features4\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Label BG\" name=\"labelBg\" value=\"#f0e4ff\" condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Colored Text\" name=\"coloredText\" value=\"#913BFF\" condition=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <select title=\"Card Amount\" name=\"lists1Amount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"showCardBg\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card color\" name=\"cardBg\" value=\"#22a5e5\" condition=\"showCardBg\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Number\" name=\"showCardNumber\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Number Color\" name=\"numberColor\" value=\"#010d4c\" condition=\"showCardNumber\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Text\" name=\"showCardText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image BG\" name=\"showImgBg\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1-2.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#060606\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-xxl-5 col-lg-6 col-md-7 col-text\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"label-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\" data-app-selector=\".label-text\"><b>Why Choose us</b></p>\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Our Approach To Each Your Business Goals</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt.</p>\n                    <div class=\"cards-container\">\n                        <div class=\"card card-1\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText\">\n                            <div class=\"card-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardNumber\">\n                                1\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"card-text-container\">\n                                <h2 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Client-centric Approach</b></h2>\n                                <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">For our company, our clientele remain at the core. As a popular Mobile App Development Company and IT solutions provider, we ensure that our stakeholders are immensely satisfied, come what may. We propel our ideas and assess them through customers' perspectives with pertinent solutions that address their business challenges.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-if=\"lists1Amount > 1\">\n                            <div class=\"card card-2\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText\">\n                                <div class=\"card-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardNumber\">\n                                    2\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card-text-container\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Effective Collaboration</b></h2>\n                                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">We never under -communicate with our clients, always maintaining a clear and precise line of communication through different media. Our communication and collaboration efforts enable smooth functioning of the project with constant feedback and inputs helping us meet the requirements to the tee. Additionally, we ensure that our clients are satisfied with the updates and can depend on our deliverables without delay.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-if=\"lists1Amount > 2\">\n                            <div class=\"card card-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText\">\n                                <div class=\"card-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardNumber\">\n                                    3\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"card-text-container\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Quality in Every Measure</b></h2>\n                                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">As a veteran IT solutions company, we ensure that our clients are promised and delivered impeccable quality solutions with robust infrastructure ideas with superior quality, at all times. Over the years, we have completed multiple projects in every domain and client testimony is proof of our constant and replicated success, defining the standards and living up to them, always.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Read More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/undraw-pie-graph-re-fvol.svg\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bg-round\" mbr-if=\"showImgBg\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"auto\" width=\"905\" height=\"1249\" viewBox=\"0 0 905 1249\" fill=\"none\">\n                    <rect x=\"-216\" y=\"838.195\" width=\"1276.24\" height=\"1112.27\" rx=\"556.137\" transform=\"rotate(-55.6916 -216 838.195)\" fill=\"url(#paint0_linear_450_257)\"></rect>\n                    <defs>\n                        <linearGradient id=\"paint0_linear_450_257\" x1=\"-146.379\" y1=\"1457.32\" x2=\"988.211\" y2=\"1457.31\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                            <stop stop-color=\"#F6FDFF\"></stop>\n                            <stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"white\" stop-opacity=\"0\"></stop>\n                        </linearGradient>\n                    </defs>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
