        },
        {
          "_name": "article06",
          "_sourceTheme": "essencem5",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "overflow": "hidden",
            "&::before": {
              "content": "''",
              "position": "absolute",
              "bottom": "0",
              "width": "200vh",
              "height": "25%",
              "background-image": "linear-gradient(transparent, @shadow 50%)",
              "z-index": "1"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@fullWidth)": {
              ".container-fluid": {
                "padding": "0 80px",
                "@media (max-width: 1200px)": {
                  "padding": "0 40px"
                },
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "0 22px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".container": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0 22px"
              }
            },
            ".row": {
              "justify-content": "center"
            },
            ".content-wrapper": {
              "position": "relative",
              "z-index": "1",
              "padding": "100px 0",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0"
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "0"
              },
              ".mbr-desc": {
                "margin-bottom": "10px"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-desc": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "text-align": "center"
            }
          },
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article06 essencem5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Description\" name=\"showDesc\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow Color\" name=\"shadow\" value=\"#000000\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/strategy-506x152.jpg\" parallax selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#000000\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1-6.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Home / Help center</b></h2>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-desc mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-desc\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showDesc\">\n                        Write to us and subscribe on our social networks\n                    </p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Сontact now\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "article06-5e",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "uwJBBKdNiI",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "form01",
          "_sourceTheme": "carem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"form01 carem5\" group=\"Form\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"12\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Description\" name=\"showDesc\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Decoration\" name=\"showDecor\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Decor Color 1\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"decor_1\" condition=\"showDecor\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Decor Color 2\" value=\"#22654e\" name=\"decor_2\" condition=\"showDecor\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Decor Color 3\" value=\"#246f55\" name=\"decor_3\" condition=\"showDecor\">\n        <header>Form</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"border\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Active BG\" value=\"#144031\" name=\"active\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/carem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#22654e\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/carem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.4\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\"></mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-8\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showDesc || showTitle\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-desc mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showDesc\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-desc\">\n                        <b>DO YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS ABOUT OUR PRODUCTS?</b>\n                    </p>\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                        Our team will quickly answer any questions!\n                    </h2>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-wrapper\">\n                    <div mbr-form class=\"mbr-form\">\n<!--Formbuilder Form-->\n<form action=\"writeus@finbytech.com\" name=\"Form Name\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\" data-verified=\"writeus@finbytech.com\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Thanks for filling out the form!</div>\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\"> Oops...! some problem! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dragArea row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3 mb-3\" data-for=\"name\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Full Name*\" data-form-field=\"name\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3 mb-3\" data-for=\"email\">\n<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email*\" data-form-field=\"email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"number\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3\">\n<input type=\"number\" name=\"number\" placeholder=\"Phone Number*\" data-form-field=\"number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" max=\"100\" min=\"0\" step=\"1\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"text1\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3\" hidden=\"hidden\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"text1\" placeholder=\"Department*\" data-form-field=\"text1\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" value hidden=\"hidden\">\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"text\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3 mb-3\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"text\" placeholder=\"Enter Your Software ID\" data-form-field=\"text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"select\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\">\n<label mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" for=\"select\" class=\"form-control-label mbr-fonts-style\">Please Select an Option. </label>\n<select name=\"select\" data-form-field=\"select\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control form-select\" placeholder=\"please select your query\">\n<option value=\"Software Not Working\">Software Not Working</option>\n<option value=\"API pending\">API pending</option>\n<option value=\"KYC Related Issue\">KYC Related Issue</option>\n<option value=\"License is Expired\">License is Expired</option>\n<option value=\"Customer Support Call Back\">Customer Support Call Back</option>\n</select>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\" data-for=\"textarea\">\n<textarea name=\"textarea\" placeholder=\"Please provide few more information! our team will call you quickly. \" data-form-field=\"textarea\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\"></textarea>\n</div>\n<div mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\" class=\"col mbr-section-btn\">\n<a data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\" type=\"submit\" class=\"w-100 w-100 w-100 w-100 w-100 btn btn-secondary\"> Send Message </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</form><!--Formbuilder Form-->\n</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"decor-wrap_1\" mbr-if=\"showDecor\"></div>\n    <div class=\"decor-wrap_2\" mbr-if=\"showDecor\"></div>\n    <div class=\"decor-wrap_3\" mbr-if=\"showDecor\"></div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "overflow": "hidden",
            "position": "relative",
            ".decor-wrap_1": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "2rem",
              "left": "18%",
              "width": "133px",
              "height": "133px",
              "border-radius": "100%",
              "background-image": "radial-gradient(165.7% 132.72% at 4.98% 5.22%, @decor_1 0, @decor_2 43%, @decor_3 100%)"
            },
            ".decor-wrap_2": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "20%",
              "right": "-4rem",
              "width": "245px",
              "height": "245px",
              "border-radius": "100%",
              "background-image": "radial-gradient(165.7% 132.72% at 4.98% 5.22%, @decor_1 0, @decor_2 43%, @decor_3 100%)"
            },
            ".decor-wrap_3": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "bottom": "-35%",
              "left": "-10rem",
              "width": "539px",
              "height": "539px",
              "border-radius": "100%",
              "background-image": "radial-gradient(165.7% 132.72% at 4.98% 5.22%, @decor_1 0, @decor_2 43%, @decor_3 100%)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@fullWidth)": {
              ".container-fluid": {
                "padding": "0 60px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "0 30px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".container": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0 30px"
              }
            },
            ".row": {
              "justify-content": "center",
              "position": "relative",
              "z-index": "1"
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              "margin-bottom": "80px",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "40px"
              },
              ".mbr-desc": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px"
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "0"
              }
            },
            ".form-wrapper": {
              ".dragArea.row": {
                "margin": "0 -30px",
                ".mbr-section-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "40px !important"
                },
                ".mbr-text": {
                  "margin-bottom": "40px !important"
                },
                ".form-group": {
                  "position": "relative",
                  "margin-bottom": "30px !important",
                  "padding": "0 30px",
                  ".form-control-label": {
                    "width": "100%",
                    "margin-bottom": "10px"
                  },
                  ".form-control": {
                    "position": "relative",
                    "z-index": "1",
                    "padding": "30px 30px 10px",
                    "border": "none !important",
                    "box-shadow": "none",
                    "border-radius": "0 !important",
                    "background-color": "transparent",
                    "border-bottom": "2px solid @border !important",
                    "transition": "all .3s ease",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "padding": "16px"
                    },
                    "&::placeholder": {
                      "color": "@border",
                      "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out"
                    },
                    "&:hover, &:focus": {
                      "background-color": "@active",
                      "&::placeholder": {
                        "opacity": ".5"
                      }
                    },
                    "textarea": {
                      "min-height": "150px"
                    },
                    ".form-check": {
                      "padding-left": "1.9em",
                      "margin-bottom": "16px",
                      ".form-check-input": {
                        "background-color": "@border",
                        "border-color": "@border",
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                ".mbr-section-btn": {
                  "width": "100%",
                  "padding": "0",
                  "margin": "0",
                  ".btn": {
                    "margin-top": "10px"
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-desc": {
              "color": "#c7fcb5",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            "LABEL": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "uwJetDz7MM",
          "_anchor": "form01-51",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#bbbbbb",
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#000000\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">Our service includes products that are traded on margin and carry a risk of losses exceeding your deposited funds. These products may not be suitable for all investors. Please ensure that you fully understand the risks involved.\n<br>\n<br>FINBYTECH IT SOLUTION (OPC) PRIVATE LIMITED is an API BRIDGE-trading platform that connects various platform like Amibroker, MT4, and TradingView to your broker via API, and help retail traders and Investor to manage their wealth smartly. Please consult your financial advisor before investing/trading via our platform. FINBYTECH IT SOLUTION (OPC) PRIVATE LIMITED is not liable for any losses that occurred due to any reason whatsoever due to our platform.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "content5-4t",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "uwJdhd5SIz",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#bbbbbb",
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#000000\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">The purpose of this report/presentation is to provide essential information about our services to assist and enable investors to make informed decisions about engaging with our platform. The presentation/report is for informational purposes only and should not be regarded as an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy the securities or other investments mentioned in it, nor should it be taken as investment advice. We do not represent that any information, including third-party information, is accurate or complete, and it should not be relied upon without proper investigation by the investor. Investments in securities/equity-related instruments are subject to market risk, which may be specific to the security or the market and can arise from company, industry, political, or economic factors, both domestic and global.\n<br>\n<br><b>Kindly Note : We are not a SEBI (Securities Exchange Board of India) registered investment advisor or Research Analyist, therefore, none of our ALGO STRATEGIES shall be considered as an investment advice. | Market participants shall use these ALGO STRATEGIES for their knowledge purposes only. | CONSULT YOUR INVESTMENT ADVISOR BEFORE INVESTING. | FINBYTECH IT SOLUTION (OPC) PRIVATE LIMITED  ISN'T LIABLE FOR YOUR PROFITS OR LOSSES. | ALL THE FEES PAID TO FINBYTECH IT SOLUTION (OPC) PRIVATE LIMITED IS NON - REFUNDABLE. Any dispute arising under these terms and conditions shall be subject to the Jhansi, UP,  Jurisdiction only. \n<br></b>\n<br>Past performance of advice, strategy, or model does not indicate future performance of any current or future strategy, model, or advice by <b>Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited</b>. Actual returns may differ significantly from those depicted herein due to various factors, including but not limited to impact costs, expenses charged, timing of entry/exit, timing of additional flows/redemptions, individual client mandates, specific portfolio construction characteristics, etc. There is no assurance or guarantee that the objectives of any strategy, model, or advice provided by <b>Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited</b> will be achieved. <b>Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited</b> or any of its partners, principal officers, or employees do not assure or guarantee any return on investments in the strategies, models, or advice given to the investor. The value of investments can go up or down depending on factors and forces affecting securities markets. Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited or its associates are not liable or responsible for any loss or shortfall arising from operations and affected by market conditions. Securities investment is subject to market risks, and Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited makes no representation, assurance, or guarantee that the objectives of any of the models, strategies, or advice on the platform or communicated will be achieved in the future. The necessary information about the investment required by an investor before investing is disclosed in the relevant advisory agreement. The investor should carefully read all terms and conditions of the agreement before subscribing to services and shall not hold Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited and/or its associates/employees liable for any risks/losses pertaining to any strategies, models, or advice launched/provided by Finbytech IT Solution (OPC) Private Limited Corporation from time to time.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
