        {
          "_name": "features05",
          "_sourceTheme": "flavorm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features05 flavorm5\" group=\"Features\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Decoration\" name=\"showDecor\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Decoration BG\" value=\"#000000\" name=\"decor\" condition=\"showDecor\" selected>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color 1\" value=\"#FFA7F1\" name=\"icon_1\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color 2\" value=\"#5CD070\" name=\"icon_2\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color 3\" value=\"#A3C2FF\" name=\"icon_3\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/flavorm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#22a5e5\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/flavorm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-2\"></div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                        <b>OneClick Features</b></h2>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"items-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image active\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_2\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont fa-laptop fa\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Customers</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>In OneClick Platform you can control &amp; limit the access for your internal team include operations, sales, franchise partners and create separate space for their users which only they can able to manage.<br><br>So you can focus on your core business activities.&nbsp; &nbsp;</b></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div><div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_1\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-users mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Range</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Create &amp; manages Unlimited Clients; <i>you </i>can decide what your clients will see in the marketplace, how many strategies they can build and which exchanges they can connect to. The best part? You never have to share your client’s contact details with us.\n<br></b>\n<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_2\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-protect mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Quality</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Adds multiple Brokers<br><br>Connect various brokers to manage trades across different platforms.\n<br></b>\n<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_3\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-user mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Team</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Perform Trade Manually For Multiple Clients</b><br><br><b>Take control when needed with manual trade options.<br>&nbsp;</b><br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_3\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-setting-3 mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Order</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Automates Your Strategy</b><br><b>Integrate any TradingView strategy for automatic execution and if you wish </b><span style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\"><b>integrate</b></span><b>&nbsp;any other platform we can do that for you.&nbsp;</b><br><br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_1\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-preview mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Design</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Set Predefined Stop-Loss and Target<br></b><br><b>Set your risk management parameters in advance for each strategies which you've created.\n<br>\n<br>&nbsp;</b><br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_2\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-hearth mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Customers</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Create separate market place for each user and automate strategies of each market place separately; best part your pricing, your branding and your growth and our success.&nbsp;</b><br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div><div class=\"item features-without-image\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card_2\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-touch mobi-mbri\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 165, 229); fill: rgb(34, 165, 229);\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                    <b>Customers</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>Increase Customer loyalty for your sub broking, IA &amp; RA businesses.&nbsp;<br><br>Algo trading will help you stand out from the competition by giving your clients something few others will have to offer.</b><br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"decor-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showDecor\"></div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "position": "relative",
            "overflow": "hidden",
            "display": "flex",
            "align-items": "center",
            ".decor-wrap": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "pointer-events": "none",
              "right": "0",
              "width": "85%",
              "height": "140%",
              "border-radius": "100% 0 0 100%",
              "background-color": "@decor",
              "@media (max-width: 1500px)": {
                "width": "90%"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "width": "100%",
                "border-radius": "0"
              },
              "& when (@reverseContent)": {
                "border-radius": "0 100% 100% 0",
                "right": "auto",
                "left": "0"
              }
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              "position": "relative",
              "z-index": "1",
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "64px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "margin-bottom": "46px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".items-wrapper": {
              "position": "relative",
              "z-index": "1",
              "display": "grid",
              "grid-template-columns": "1fr 1fr 1fr",
              "gap": "64px",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "display": "block"
              }
            },
            ".item": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "46px"
              },
              ".item-wrapper": {
                ".card-box": {
                  ".icon-wrapper": {
                    "margin-bottom": "22px",
                    ".mbr-iconfont": {
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "font-size": "64px"
                    }
                  },
                  ".item-title": {
                    "margin-bottom": "16px"
                  },
                  ".item-text": {
                    "margin-bottom": "0"
                  }
                }
              },
              ".card_1": {
                ".card-box .icon-wrapper .mbr-iconfont": {
                  "color": "@icon_1"
                }
              },
              ".card_2": {
                ".card-box .icon-wrapper .mbr-iconfont": {
                  "color": "@icon_2"
                }
              },
              ".card_3": {
                ".card-box .icon-wrapper .mbr-iconfont": {
                  "color": "@icon_3"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#22a5e5",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".item-title": {
              "color": "#212529"
            },
            ".item-text": {
              "color": "#51565c"
            },
            ".item-text, .icon-wrapper": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "uWK7CN6Uwb",
          "_anchor": "features05-at",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "slider02",
          "_sourceTheme": "walletm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"slider02 mbr-embla walletm5\" group=\"Sliders & Galleries\" plugins=\"embla\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>Carousel</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Autoplay\" name=\"autoplay\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Interval\" name=\"interval\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" value=\"5\" step=\"1\" condition=\"autoplay\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Loop\" name=\"loop\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Draggable\" name=\"draggable\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"arrows\" title=\"Arrows\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"arrowsMobile\" title=\"Mobile Arrows\" condition=\"arrows\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Arrows Color\" value=\"#02050a\" name=\"arrowsColor\" condition=\"arrows\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Arrows BG\" value=\"#f5f8ff\" name=\"arrowsBg\" condition=\"arrows\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Shadow\" name=\"showShadow\" checked condition=\"bg.type == 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow Color\" value=\"#02050a\" name=\"shadow\" condition=\"showShadow && bg.type == 'color'\" checked>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"gap\" title=\"Gap\" min=\"0\" max=\"30\" step=\"6\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Text\" name=\"showCardText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" value=\"#22a5e5\" name=\"cardBg\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax required>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/walletm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#02050a\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#f4f4f4\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\" class=\"content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Power Packed Features</b><br></h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"embla\" data-loop=\"{{loop}}\" data-auto-play=\"{{autoplay}}\" data-auto-play-interval=\"{{interval}}\" data-draggable=\"{{draggable}}\" data-skip-snaps=\"true\" data-align=\"center\" data-contain-scroll=\"trimSnaps\">\n                    <div class=\"embla__viewport\">\n                        <div class=\"embla__container\">\n                            <div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item features-without-image active\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'px', 'margin-right': gap + 'px'}\">\n                                <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                                    <div class=\"item-wrapper little-radius\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n                                            <b>Admin Dashboard</b></h4>\n                                        <div class=\"item-content\">\n                                            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\">Get full access to manage users, brokers, and trades from a centralized console.<br></p>\n                                            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                                <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-black\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    Read more\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div><div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item features-without-image\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'px', 'margin-right': gap + 'px'}\">\n                                <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                                    <div class=\"item-wrapper little-radius\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Multi Orders</b></h4>\n                                        <div class=\"item-content\">\n                                            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\">OneClick and Place orders across multiple accounts.&nbsp;</p>\n                                            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                                <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-black\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    Read more\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            \n                            \n                            <div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item features-without-image\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'px', 'margin-right': gap + 'px'}\">\n                                <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                                    <div class=\"item-wrapper little-radius\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Custom UI Design</b></h4>\n                                        <div class=\"item-content\">\n                                            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\">Custom UI design that adapts your brand across every digital channel.<br></p>\n                                            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                                <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-black\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                                    Read more\n                                                </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <button class=\"embla__button embla__button--prev\">\n                        <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-left mbr-iconfont\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                        <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden\">Previous</span>\n                    </button>\n                    <button class=\"embla__button embla__button--next\">\n                        <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                        <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden visually-hidden\">Next</span>\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "display": "inline-block",
                "width": "70%",
                "margin-bottom": "84px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "width": "100%",
                  "margin-bottom": "48px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".embla__slide": {
              "display": "flex",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "position": "relative",
              "min-width": "466px",
              "max-width": "466px",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "min-width": "100%",
                "max-width": "100%"
              },
              ".slide-content": {
                "width": "100%",
                ".item-wrapper": {
                  "min-height": "540px",
                  "height": "100%",
                  "background-color": "@cardBg",
                  "padding": "30px",
                  "display": "flex",
                  "flex-direction": "column",
                  "justify-content": "space-between",
                  "@media (max-width: 1440px)": {
                    "min-height": "auto"
                  },
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "padding": "24px"
                  },
                  ".card-title": {
                    "margin-bottom": "48px",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "margin-bottom": "24px"
                    }
                  },
                  ".item-content": {
                    ".card-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    },
                    ".mbr-section-btn": {
                      "margin-top": "48px",
                      "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                        "margin-top": "24px"
                      },
                      ".btn": {
                        "margin-bottom": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".embla__button--next, .embla__button--prev": {
              "display": "flex"
            },
            ".embla__button": {
              "bottom": "0",
              "width": "64px",
              "height": "64px",
              "font-size": "32px",
              "background-color": "@arrowsBg !important",
              "color": "@arrowsColor !important",
              "border": "none !important",
              "border-radius": "100%",
              "transition": "all 0.3s",
              "position": "absolute",
              "display": "flex",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "align-items": "center",
              "opacity": "1 !important",
              "& when not (@arrows)": {
                "display": "none"
              },
              "& when not (@arrowsMobile)": {
                "@media (max-width: 768px)": {
                  "display": "none"
                }
              },
              "&:hover": {
                "opacity": ".8 !important"
              },
              "&:disabled": {
                "opacity": ".2 !important"
              },
              "&.embla__button--prev": {
                "margin-left": "-74px"
              },
              "&.embla__button--next": {
                "margin-right": "-74px"
              }
            },
            ".embla": {
              "position": "relative",
              "width": "100%",
              "display": "flex",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "& when (@arrows)": {
                "padding-bottom": "8rem",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding-bottom": "6rem"
                }
              },
              "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
                "& when (@showShadow)": {
                  "&::before": {
                    "content": "''",
                    "position": "absolute",
                    "top": "0",
                    "left": "0",
                    "width": "25%",
                    "height": "100%",
                    "background-image": "linear-gradient(90deg, @shadow 50%, transparent)",
                    "pointer-events": "none",
                    "z-index": "1",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "display": "none"
                    }
                  },
                  "&::after": {
                    "content": "''",
                    "position": "absolute",
                    "top": "0",
                    "right": "0",
                    "width": "25%",
                    "height": "100%",
                    "background-image": "linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, @shadow 50%)",
                    "pointer-events": "none",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "display": "none"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".embla__viewport": {
              "overflow": "hidden",
              "width": "100%",
              "margin-right": "1rem"
            },
            ".embla__viewport.is-draggable": {
              "cursor": "grab"
            },
            ".embla__viewport.is-dragging": {
              "cursor": "grabbing"
            },
            ".embla__container": {
              "display": "flex",
              "user-select": "none",
              "-webkit-touch-callout": "none",
              "-khtml-user-select": "none",
              "-webkit-tap-highlight-color": "transparent"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper": {
              "color": "#f5f8ff",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".card-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".card-text": {
              "color": "#000000",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".card-title, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "text-align": "center",
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "uWKCybo4jh",
          "_anchor": "slider02-az",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = \"color\")": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = \"image\")": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)",
              "& when (@overlay)": {
                ".mbr-overlay": {
                  "background": "@overlayColor",
                  "opacity": "@overlayOpacity"
                }
              }
            },
            ".item-img": {
              "position": "relative",
              "img": {
                "transition": "all 0.2s",
                "object-fit": "cover"
              }
            },
            ".cardbg": {
              "background": "@contentBg",
              "height": "100%",
              "min-height": "160px"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "border": "1px solid currentColor",
              "border-radius": "1rem",
              "width": "fit-content",
              "padding": "0.2rem 0.7rem",
              "display": "inline-block"
            },
            ".image-wrapper": {
              "overflow": "hidden"
            },
            ".item1": {
              "margin-bottom": "2rem !important"
            },
            ".item-wrapper": {
              "position": "relative",
              "background": "@cardsBg",
              "border": "3px solid @cardsBg",
              "overflow": "hidden",
              "height": "100%",
              "display": "flex",
              "flex-flow": "column nowrap",
              ".item-footer": {
                "margin-top": "auto"
              }
            },
            ".item-link": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "bottom": "8px",
              "right": "90px",
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".item1, .item": {
              "transition": "transform 0.3s",
              ".item": {
                "&:hover": {
                  "cursor": "pointer"
                }
              },
              "&:hover": {
                ".link-icon-wrapper span": {
                  "transform": "rotate(-20deg) scale(1.3)"
                }
              },
              "margin-bottom": "2rem"
            },
            ".card2": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-top": "1rem"
              }
            },
            ".link-icon-wrapper": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "right": "-1px",
              "padding": "2px",
              "bottom": "-1px",
              "background": "@cardsBg",
              "width": "68px",
              "height": "68px",
              "display": "flex",
              "justify-content": "flex-end",
              "align-items": "flex-end",
              "border-top-left-radius": "50%",
              "border-bottom-right-radius": "2rem",
              "z-index": "3",
              ".icon-wrap": {
                "background": "@iconBg",
                "width": "55px",
                "height": "55px",
                "transition": "all 0.3s",
                "display": "flex",
                "justify-content": "center",
                "align-items": "center",
                "border-radius": "50%",
                "span": {
                  "color": "@iconColor",
                  "font-size": "1.1rem",
                  "transition": "all 0.3s",
                  "display": "block",
                  "padding-top": "1px"
                }
              },
              ".svg1": {
                "position": "absolute",
                "top": "-29px",
                "right": "0px",
                "transform": "rotate(180deg)",
                "width": "30px",
                "path": {
                  "fill": "@cardsBg"
                }
              },
              ".svg2": {
                "position": "absolute",
                "transform": "rotate(180deg)",
                "width": "30px",
                "bottom": "0",
                "left": "-29px",
                "path": {
                  "fill": "@cardsBg"
                }
              }
            },
            ".item-content": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "left": "0",
              "margin-top": "1rem",
              "padding": "0 1.5rem 2rem",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "padding": "0 1rem 1.4rem",
                "margin-top": "1rem"
              },
              "display": "flex",
              "flex-direction": "column",
              "height": "100%"
            },
            "img, .item-img": {
              "width": "100%"
            },
            ".item:focus, span:focus": {
              "outline": "none"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".item": {
                "margin-bottom": "1rem"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000000",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".item-title": {
              "text-align": "left",
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".item-subtitle": {
              "text-align": "left",
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle, .subtitle-wrap, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "text-align": "left",
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "contacts2",
          "_sourceTheme": "ascentm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"ascentm5 contacts2\" group=\"contacts\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\">\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showLink\" title=\"Link\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsBg\" title=\"Card BG\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"contentBg\" title=\"Content BG\" value=\"#22a5e5\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconBg\" title=\"Icon BG\" value=\"#000000\">\n\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" required>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/ascentm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle || showmainButton\">\n                    <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                        <b>Title</b>\n                    </h4>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"row\">\n\n\n            <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\n                <div class=\"row h-100\">\n\n                    <div class=\"item features-image h-100 col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 active\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper card2 h-100\">\n                            <div class=\"item-img h-100\">\n                                <div class=\"cardbg\">\n\n                                </div>\n\n                                <div class=\"link-icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <svg class=\"svg1\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                                        <path d=\"m100,0H0v100C0,44.77,44.77,0,100,0Z\"></path>\n                                    </svg>\n\n                                    <div class=\"icon-wrap\">\n                                        <a href=\"popup:#mbr-popup-c8\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#mbr-popup-c8\" data-bs-target=\"#mbr-popup-c8\"><span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn mobi-mbri-right mobi-mbri\"></span></a>\n                                    </div>\n\n                                    <svg class=\"svg2\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                                        <path d=\"m100,0H0v100C0,44.77,44.77,0,100,0Z\"></path>\n                                    </svg>\n\n                                </div>\n\n                                <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                                    <div class=\"subtitle-wrap mb-3 w-100\">\n                                        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .subtitle-wrap, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                                            Our\n                                            Services</h5>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Let's sign-up for book a demo.&nbsp;</b></h5>\n\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\">\n                                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse a lacus non\n                                        elit pretium\n                                        tristique. Proin pulvinar placerat mi, sed maximus sapien bibendum eu. Duis vel\n                                        lorem sagittis,\n                                        commodo enim nec, vulputate sapien.&nbsp;</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-link mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-link\" mbr-if=\"showLink\">\n                                    <div><br></div>\n                                    <div><b><a href=\"popup:#mbr-popup-c8\" class=\"text-primary\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#mbr-popup-c8\" data-bs-target=\"#mbr-popup-c8\">Sign-up</a></b></div>\n                                </h4>\n\n                            </div>\n\n\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n\n\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uWKEiQ2RC9",
          "_anchor": "contacts2-b0",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "list01",
          "_sourceTheme": "emblemm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"list01 emblemm5\" group=\"List\" plugins=\"mbr-switch-arrow, mobirise-icons2\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Description\" name=\"showDesc\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Email\" name=\"showEmail\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" value=\"#1f2329\" name=\"cardBg\" selected>\n        <header>List</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"5\">5</option>\n            <option value=\"6\" selected>6</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"icon\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" value=\"#1f2329\" name=\"iconBg\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"border\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gradient Background\" name=\"gradientBg\" condition=\"bg.type=='color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Gradient Color\" name=\"gradientColor\" value=\"#22a5e5\" condition=\"gradientBg &&bg.type=='color'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                        FAQ's</h2>\n                    <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"card-wrap\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-desc mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-desc, .card-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showDesc\">\n                                <b>Get in touch with us now!</b>\n                            </p>\n                            <a href=\"#\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-email mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showEmail\"><a href=\"mailto:sales@finbytechnovation.in\" class=\"text-info\">sales@finbytechnovation.in</a></p>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-7\">\n                <div id=\"bootstrap-accordion\" class=\"panel-group accordionStyles accordion\" role=\"tablist\" aria-multiselectable=\"true\">\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse1\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n                                    What is OneClick Trade Platform</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">A powerful white-label admin dashboard designed to simplify multi-account management and automation for traders and sub-brokers, RA, and IA.\n<br>\n<br>✅ Effortlessly integrate and control all your broker accounts in one place.\n<br>✅ Place a single trade, mirror it across unlimited client accounts.\n<br>✅ Turn TradingView strategies into fully automated trades.\n<br>✅ Power system for your all trading needs \n<br>\n<br>Save time and scale your algo business effortlessly with your own algo platform powered by Finbytechnovation</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingTwo\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse2\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Does this platform automate strategies is user accounts ?&nbsp;</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingTwo\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">yes, via webhook and internal trade manage platform you can create automate strategies which will place trade also user of <i>the </i>platform can also create strategies and deploy in their panel.&nbsp;</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingThree\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse3\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">What Features are available in Oneclick Trading Platform for B2B</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingThree\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">In OneClick Platform you can control &amp; limit the access for your internal team include operations, sales, franchise partners and create separate space for their users which only they can able to manage.\n<br>\n<br>So you can focus on your core business activities.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 3\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFour\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse4\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">What control we can have over our platform ?&nbsp;</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFour\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Create &amp; manages Unlimited Clients; you can decide what your clients will see in the marketplace, how many strategies they can build and which exchanges they can connect to. The best part? You never have to share your client’s contact details with us.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 4\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingFive\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse5\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n                                    What are your charges and costing for platform ?&nbsp;</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingFive\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Costs vary based on the services you require. We offer competitive pricing and can provide a detailed quote after understanding your development scope.<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 5\">\n                        <div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingSix\">\n                            <a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse6\">\n                                <h4 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n                                    How to book demo of your software ?&nbsp;</h4>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-plus mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingSix\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n                                <p class=\"panel-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">\n                                    You can call us on number or your can fill our demo form; our experts will get in touch with you.&nbsp;</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value",
              "& when (@gradientBg)": {
                "background-image": "linear-gradient(45deg, @gradientColor -20%, @bg-value 40%)",
                "@media (max-width: 768px)": {
                  "background-image": "linear-gradient(45deg, @gradientColor -60%, @bg-value 40%)"
                }
              }
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".row": {
              "justify-content": "space-between"
            },
            ".content-wrapper": {
              "height": "100%",
              "display": "flex",
              "flex-direction": "column",
              "justify-content": "space-between",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "22px",
                "height": "auto"
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "22px"
              },
              ".card-wrapper": {
                "-webkit-flex": "inherit",
                ".card-wrap": {
                  "display": "inline-block",
                  "padding": "32px 26px",
                  "background-color": "@cardBg",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "padding": "16px"
                  },
                  ".mbr-desc": {
                    "margin-bottom": "10px"
                  },
                  ".mbr-email": {
                    "margin-bottom": "0"
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".panel-group": {
              ".card": {
                "position": "relative",
                "padding": "22px 0 26px 0",
                "background-color": "transparent",
                "border-bottom": "1px solid @border",
                "border-radius": "0 !important",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "16px 0 16px 0"
                },
                "&:first-child": {
                  "border-top": "1px solid @border"
                },
                ".card-header": {
                  "background-color": "transparent",
                  "border": "none",
                  "border-radius": "0",
                  "padding": "0",
                  ".panel-title": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    "justify-content": "space-between",
                    "align-items": "center",
                    "width": "100%",
                    ".panel-title-edit": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    },
                    ".icon-wrapper": {
                      "width": "32px",
                      "height": "32px",
                      "min-width": "32px",
                      "display": "inline-flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "margin-left": "16px",
                      "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                      "border-radius": "5px",
                      "background-color": "@iconBg",
                      ".mbr-iconfont": {
                        "font-size": "18px",
                        "transition": "all 0.3s ease-in-out",
                        "color": "@icon"
                      }
                    },
                    "&:not(.collapsed)": {
                      ".icon-wrapper": {
                        ".mbr-iconfont": {
                          "transform": "rotate(-45deg)"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                ".panel-collapse": {
                  ".panel-body": {
                    "margin-top": "22px",
                    ".panel-text": {
                      "margin-bottom": "0"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-desc": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-email": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".panel-title-edit": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".panel-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "uWKFvvQNNf",
          "_anchor": "list01-b2",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "footer03",
          "_sourceTheme": "cryptom5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"footer3\" group=\"Footers\" global once=\"footer\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-reveal': reveal, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reveal effect\" name=\"reveal\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Form\" name=\"showForm\" checked>\n        <header condition=\"showForm\">Form</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Input BG\" name=\"inputBg\" value=\"#22a5e5\" condition=\"showForm\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Input Text\" name=\"inputTextColor\" value=\"#bbbbbb\" condition=\"showForm\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/cryptom5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#333333\" condition=\"overlay&&bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay&&bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <!-- End block parameters -->\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay&&bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-left justify-content-center mbr-white\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 md-pb\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Quick links</b></h2>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mbr-lighter\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><a href=\"Terms and condition.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Terms &amp; Condition</a><br><a href=\"Privacy & Policies.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Privacy &amp; Policy&nbsp;</a><br>✓ Disclaimer<br><a href=\"page21.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Refund Policy&nbsp;</a><br>✓ White-label Agreement<br>✓ Refer &amp; Earn Policy&nbsp;<br><a href=\"KYC POLICIES.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ KYC Disclaimer&nbsp;</a><div><br></div></h3>\n\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 md-pb\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>\n                        Services &amp; Products</b></h2>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mbr-lighter\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><a href=\"index.html#afeatures2-9q\" class=\"text-info text-primary\">✓ Digital Marketing</a><br><a href=\"index.html#afeatures2-9r\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Web Development</a><br><a href=\"index.html#afeatures2-9t\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Mobile App Development</a><br><a href=\"oneclick.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ OneClick Trade Manager</a><br><a href=\"courses.html\" class=\"text-info\">✓ Educational Courses&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><div><a href=\"oneclick.html\" class=\"text-info\"><br></a><br><br></div></h3>\n\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 md-pb\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .icons-wrapper\"><b>\n                        Links</b></h2>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mbr-lighter\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-info\">Home</a><br><a href=\"about us.html\" class=\"text-info\">About</a><br><a href=\"oneclick.html\" class=\"text-info\">Products</a><br><a href=\"Contact us.html\" class=\"text-info\">Contact us&nbsp;</a><br><a href=\"Payment.html\" class=\"text-info\">Make Payment</a><a href=\"Contact us.html\" class=\"text-info\"><br></a></h3>\n\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3 md-pb\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .icons-wrapper\"><b>We're always here to help</b></h2>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mbr-lighter\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .icons-wrapper\">Subscribe to our newsletter to get updated information.</h3>\n                <div mbr-form class=\"form1 px-2\" mbr-if=\"showForm\">\n                    <!--Formbuilder Form-->\n                    <form action=\"info@finbytechnovation.in\" name=\"My Mobirise Form\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\" data-verified=\"info@finbytechnovation.in\">\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Thanks for filling\n                                out the form!</div>\n                            <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"dragArea row\">\n                            <div class=\"col form-group \" data-for=\"email\">\n                                <input type=\"text\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"E-mail\" data-form-field=\"E-mail\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" required=\"required\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-auto mbr-section-btn\" mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\"><a type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">&gt;</a></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </form>\n                    <!--Formbuilder Form-->\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "& when (@bg-type = \"image\")": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = \"color\")": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "letter-spacing": "1px",
              "margin-bottom": "1rem",
              "color": "#22a5e5"
            },
            ".first-column .mbr-text": {
              "margin": "0"
            },
            ".form-group": {
              "max-width": "55%"
            },
            ".form-group, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "margin": "0",
              "padding": "0",
              "display": "-webkit-flex"
            },
            ".form-control": {
              "font-size": "0.9rem",
              "border-top-left-radius": "1rem",
              "border-bottom-left-radius": "1rem",
              "border-top-right-radius": "0 !important",
              "border-bottom-right-radius": "0 !important",
              "border": "none !important",
              "width": "100%",
              "padding": "0.3rem 1rem",
              "background": "@inputBg",
              "color": "@inputTextColor",
              "&::-webkit-input-placeholder": {
                "color": "@inputTextColor"
              },
              "&::-moz-placeholder": {
                "color": "@inputTextColor"
              },
              "&:-moz-placeholder": {
                "color": "@inputTextColor"
              },
              "&:-ms-input-placeholder": {
                "color": "@inputTextColor"
              },
              "&:hover, &:focus": {
                "border": "none !important"
              }
            },
            ".col + .mbr-section-btn .btn, .col-auto + .mbr-section-btn .btn": {
              "margin": "0 !important",
              "height": "100%",
              "border-top-right-radius": "1rem !important",
              "border-bottom-right-radius": "1rem !important",
              "border-top-left-radius": "0 !important",
              "border-bottom-left-radius": "0 !important",
              "padding": "0 2.2rem !important"
            },
            ".dragArea > *:nth-last-child(2).col, .dragArea > *:nth-last-child(2).col-auto, .col + .mbr-section-btn, .col-auto + .mbr-section-btn": {
              "padding-left": "0",
              "padding-right": "0",
              "margin": "0"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".mbr-form .row": {
                "-webkit-justify-content": "center",
                "justify-content": "center"
              }
            }
          },
          "_cid": "uWcVKVLHt9",
          "_anchor": "footer03-ai",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": true,
          "_once": "footer",
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": "popup-builder",
          "_isSecondary": true,
          "typeCompatible": "!isAMP",
          "_styles": {
            "&.popup-builder": {
              "background-color": "#ffffff",
              ".modal": {
                "position": "relative",
                "display": "block",
                "z-index": "1"
              },
              ".modal-dialog": {
                "margin-top": "60px",
                "margin-bottom": "60px",
                "& when (@popupSize = '5')": {
                  "margin-top": "0",
                  "margin-bottom": "0",
                  "margin": "0",
                  "height": "100%"
                }
              }
            },
            ".modal-content, .modal-dialog": {
              "height": "auto"
            },
            ".form-wrapper": {
              ".input-group-btn": {
                "margin-right": "auto",
                "margin-left": "auto",
                ".btn": {
                  "margin": "0 !important"
                }
              },
              "@media (min-width: 769px)": {
                ".mbr-form": {
                  ".form-group, .input-group-btn": {
                    "padding": "0 .5rem"
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".card-img": {
              "width": "100%",
              "margin": "auto",
              "border-radius": "0"
            },
            ".mbr-figure": {
              "img": {
                "display": "block",
                "width": "100%",
                "-ms-flex-item-align": "center",
                "-ms-grid-row-align": "center",
                "-webkit-align-self": "center",
                "align-self": "center"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".pt-0": {
              "padding-top": "0 !important"
            },
            ".pb-0": {
              "padding-bottom": "0 !important"
            },
            ".form-content": {
              "-ms-flex-pack": "center",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-overlay": {
              "bottom": "0",
              "left": "0",
              "position": "absolute",
              "right": "0",
              "top": "0",
              "z-index": "0",
              "pointer-events": "none"
            },
            ".modal-open": {
              "overflow": "hidden"
            },
            ".modal-open .modal": {
              "overflow-x": "hidden",
              "overflow-y": "auto"
            },
            ".modal": {
              "position": "fixed",
              "top": "0",
              "left": "0",
              "z-index": "1050",
              "display": "none",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "overflow": "hidden",
              "outline": "0"
            },
            ".modal-dialog": {
              "position": "relative",
              "width": "auto",
              "margin": ".5rem",
              "pointer-events": "none",
              "& when (@popupSize = '5')": {
                "max-width": "100%",
                "height": "100%",
                "margin": "0"
              }
            },
            ".modal.fade .modal-dialog": {
              "transition": "transform 0.3s ease-out, -webkit-transform 0.3s ease-out",
              "-webkit-transform": "translate(0, -50px)",
              "transform": "translate(0, -50px)"
            },
            ".modal.show .modal-dialog": {
              "-webkit-transform": "none",
              "transform": "none"
            },
            ".modal-dialog-centered": {
              "display": "flex",
              "-ms-flex-align": "center",
              "align-items": "center",
              "min-height": "~\"calc(100% - (.5rem * 2))\""
            },
            ".modal-dialog-centered::before": {
              "display": "block",
              "height": "~\"calc(100vh - (.5rem * 2))\"",
              "content": "\"\""
            },
            ".modal-content": {
              "background": "@cardBg",
              "position": "relative",
              "display": "flex",
              "-ms-flex-direction": "column",
              "flex-direction": "column",
              "width": "100%",
              "pointer-events": "auto",
              "background-clip": "padding-box",
              "border": "none",
              "outline": "0",
              "-webkit-box-shadow": "0 10px 40px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)",
              "box-shadow": "0 10px 40px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)",
              "& when (@popupSize = '5')": {
                "border-radius": "0",
                "height": "100%",
                "overflow": "auto"
              }
            },
            ".margin-center-pos": {
              "margin-top": "auto",
              "margin-bottom": "auto"
            },
            ".modal-backdrop": {
              "position": "fixed",
              "top": "0",
              "left": "0",
              "z-index": "1040",
              "width": "100vw",
              "height": "100vh",
              "background-color": "#000"
            },
            ".modal-backdrop.fade": {
              "opacity": "0"
            },
            ".modal-backdrop.show": {
              "opacity": ".5"
            },
            ".modal-header": {
              "display": "flex",
              "-ms-flex-align": "start",
              "align-items": "flex-start",
              "-ms-flex-pack": "justify",
              "justify-content": "space-between",
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "2rem 2rem 1rem"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "padding": "1rem"
              },
              "border-bottom": "none"
            },
            ".modal-header .close": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "1rem",
              "right": "1rem",
              "margin": "-1rem -1rem -1rem auto",
              "padding": "1rem",
              "opacity": ".75",
              "svg": {
                "fill": "@closeButton"
              },
              "&:hover": {
                "opacity": "1"
              },
              "&:focus": {
                "outline": "none"
              }
            },
            ".modal-title": {
              "line-height": "1.5",
              "width": "100%",
              "margin": "0",
              "text-align": "center",
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".modal-body": {
              "position": "relative",
              "-ms-flex": "1 1 auto",
              "flex": "1 1 auto",
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "1rem 2rem 2rem"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "padding": "1rem"
              }
            },
            ".modal-footer": {
              "display": "flex",
              "-ms-flex-align": "center",
              "align-items": "center",
              "-ms-flex-pack": "center",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0rem 2rem 2rem"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "padding": "1rem"
              },
              "border-top": "none",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".modal-scrollbar-measure": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "-9999px",
              "width": "50px",
              "height": "50px",
              "overflow": "scroll"
            },
            "@media (min-width: 576px)": {
              ".modal-dialog": {
                "& when not (@popupSize = '5')": {
                  "max-width": "500px",
                  "margin": "1.75rem auto"
                }
              },
              ".modal-dialog-centered": {
                "min-height": "~\"calc(100% - (1.75rem * 2))\""
              },
              ".modal-dialog-centered::before": {
                "height": "~\"calc(100vh - (1.75rem * 2))\""
              },
              ".modal-sm": {
                "max-width": "300px"
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
              ".modal-lg, .modal-xl": {
                "max-width": "800px"
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 1200px)": {
              ".modal-xl": {
                "max-width": "1140px"
              }
            },
            ".row": {
              "display": "flex",
              "-ms-flex-wrap": "wrap",
              "flex-wrap": "wrap",
              "margin-right": "-15px",
              "margin-left": "-15px"
            },
            ".col-md-4": {
              "position": "relative",
              "width": "100%",
              "padding-right": "15px",
              "padding-left": "15px",
              "-ms-flex": "0 0 33.333333%",
              "flex": "0 0 33.333333%",
              "max-width": "33.333333%"
            },
            ".form-group": {
              "margin-bottom": "1rem"
            },
            ".form-control": {
              "display": "block",
              "width": "100%",
              "font-size": "1rem",
              "font-weight": "400",
              "line-height": "1.5"
            },
            ".col": {
              "-ms-flex-preferred-size": "0",
              "flex-basis": "0",
              "-ms-flex-positive": "1",
              "flex-grow": "1",
              "max-width": "100%"
            },
            ".col-md-auto": {
              "position": "relative",
              "padding-right": "15px",
              "padding-left": "15px",
              "-ms-flex": "0 0 auto",
              "flex": "0 0 auto",
              "width": "auto",
              "max-width": "100%"
            },
            ".mbr-section-btn": {
              "margin": "0",
              ".btn": {
                "margin": "0"
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "mbr-popup",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"popup-builder\" group=\"Popup\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <header>Triggers / Show Popup</header>\n        <label>On Click</label>\n        <label>Use [popup-id] with any link or button (Link -&gt; Popup tab)</label>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"On Timer\" name=\"onTimer\">\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Delay (s)\" name=\"onTimerDelay\" min=\"0\" max=\"30\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"onTimer == true\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"On Page Exit\" name=\"onPageExit\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"On Scroll to End\" name=\"onScroll\">\n\n        <select title=\"Add to Pages:\" name=\"popupOnPages\" multiple condition=\"onTimer == true || onPageExit == true || onScroll == true\"></select>\n\n        <header>Content</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\">\n\n        <select title=\"Content Type\" name=\"popupContentType\">\n            <option value=\"1\">None</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">Image</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">Video</option>\n            <option value=\"4\" selected>Form</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <select title=\"Size\" name=\"popupSize\">\n            <option value=\"1\">Small</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>Default</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">Large</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">Extra large</option>\n            <option value=\"5\">Full Screen</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"cardBg\" value=\"#2380ae\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Close Button\" name=\"closeButton\" value=\"#e43f3f\">\n\n        <header>Overlay</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"popupOverlayColor\" value=\"#000000\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\">\n        <!-- End block parameters -->\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\"></mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': popupOverlayColor, 'top': 0, 'right': 0, 'bottom': 0, 'left': 0, 'position': absolute, 'z-index': 0, 'pointer-events': none}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"modal mbr-popup\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" data-overlay-color=\"{{popupOverlayColor}}\" data-overlay-opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" data-on-timer-delay=\"{{onTimer ? onTimerDelay : ''}}\" data-on-exit=\"{{onPageExit}}\" data-on-scroll=\"{{onScroll}}\">\n        <div class=\"modal-dialog\" role=\"document\" mbr-class=\"{\n            'modal-sm': popupSize == 1,\n            '': popupSize == 2,\n            'modal-lg': popupSize == 3,\n            'modal-xl': popupSize == 4\n            }\">\n            <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                <div class=\"container position-static margin-center-pos\">\n                    <div class=\"modal-header\" mbr-class=\"{'pb-0': showTitle && showText}\">\n                        <h5 class=\"modal-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".modal-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Fill your requirements&nbsp;</b></h5>\n                        <button type=\"button\" class=\"close d-flex\" data-dismiss=\"modal\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\">\n                            <svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"23\" height=\"23\" viewBox=\"0 0 23 23\" fill=\"currentColor\">\n                                <path d=\"M13.4 12l10.3 10.3-1.4 1.4L12 13.4 1.7 23.7.3 22.3 10.6 12 .3 1.7 1.7.3 12 10.6 22.3.3l1.4 1.4L13.4 12z\">\n                                </path>\n                            </svg>\n                        </button>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                            Please fill</p>\n\n                        <div mbr-if=\"popupContentType !== 1\">\n                            <div class=\"card-img mbr-figure\" mbr-if=\"popupContentType == 2\">\n                                <img src=\"../_images/popup.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n                            </div>\n                            <div mbr-video class=\"video-block mbr-figure\" mbr-if=\"popupContentType == 3\">\n                                <iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\"></iframe>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div mbr-form mbr-if=\"popupContentType == 4\" class=\"form-wrapper\">\n<!--Formbuilder Form-->\n<form action name=\"Mobirise Form\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\">\n<div class>\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\"> Thanks for filling out the form!</div>\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dragArea row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\" data-for=\"name\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Name\" data-form-field=\"Name\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" required=\"required\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group \" data-for=\"email\">\n<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" data-form-field=\"Email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" required=\"required\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"lastName\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"lastName\" placeholder=\"Contact Number\" data-form-field=\"Last Name\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" required=\"required\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"text\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"text\" placeholder=\"City\" data-form-field=\"text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" required=\"required\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"textarea\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\">\n<textarea name=\"textarea\" placeholder=\"Please specify your requirement in few details\" data-form-field=\"textarea\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\"></textarea>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-auto input-group-btn\" mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\"><a type=\"submit\" class=\"w-100 w-100 btn btn-success\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-hearth mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>Submit</a></div>\n</div>\n</form><!--Formbuilder Form-->\n</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"modal-footer\" mbr-class=\"{'pt-0': popupContentType == 1 || popupContentType == 4}\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\">\n                                LEARN MORE\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uWLRiC9RTM",
          "_anchor": "mbr-popup-c9",
          "_popupId": "mbr-popup-bn",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    "page21.html": {
      "settings": {
        "title": "Refundpolicy",
        "order": "19",
        "meta_descr": "All sales are final. Because FINBYTECH IT SOLUTIONS offers a Expert Advice evaluation to ensure that our products and services will meet your needs without the need to purchase, there will be ABSOLUTELY NO REFUNDS and CANCELLATIONS.\n\nBefore deciding to subscribe to our services, please make sure to take our Expert Advice, the evaluation version that we provide. We do not offer refunds on subscriptions that have already been taken. We so believe in our services and support.\n\nFor this reason, we strongly recommend that before payment, our visitors:-\n\nFor this reason, we strongly recommend that before payment, our visitors:-\n\nRead all information about our products, services and support given to our clients.\nEvaluate the quality of our services by taking our Expert Advice.\nRead all About Us and our technical Team.\nRead our Terms of Use.\nRead our Privacy Policy.\n\nTerms and Conditions:\n\nPlease read these terms and conditions carefully before purchasing and using our services. By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please refrain from using our services.\n\n\n1. Non-Refundable Services:\nAll our services, including the purchase of our software, are non-refundable. Once the purchase is made, it is considered final and non-cancellable. We do not provide refunds, in part or in full, for any reason, including but not limited to dissatisfaction with the software, inability to achieve desired results, or financial losses incurred while using our services.\n\n\n2. Evaluation and Research:\nWe highly recommend that you thoroughly evaluate our services, including reading our documentation, reviews, and any available trial versions before making a purchase. It is your responsibility to ensure that our software aligns with your requirements and meets your expectations. We do not guarantee specific outcomes, profitability, or suitability of our services for your specific investment goals or trading strategies.\n\n\n3. Use of Software: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE\nUpon purchasing our software, you are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the software for your personal or business purposes, subject to the terms and conditions outlined herein. You may not distribute, modify, reverse engineer, or resell the software without prior written consent from us.\n\n\n4. Risk Disclosure: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE\nTrading and investing in financial markets carry inherent risks, including the potential for substantial financial losses. We do not provide any guarantee or assurance of profitability or specific investment returns through the use of our software. It is essential that you understand the risks involved and carefully consider your financial situation and risk tolerance before using our services.\n\n\n5. Indemnification: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE By using our services, you agree to indemnify and hold us harmless from any claims, losses, damages, liabilities, and expenses arising from your use of the software or any violation of these terms and conditions.\n\n\n6. Intellectual Property:\nAll intellectual property rights, including copyrights and trademarks, associated with our services, software, documentation, and any related materials, belong to us or our licensors. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any of our intellectual property without obtaining prior written consent from us.\n\n\n7. Limitation of Liability: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE\nIn no event shall we be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to the use of our services, including but not limited to financial losses, business interruption, or loss of data.\n\n\n8. Modification of Terms: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE\nWe reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website. It is your responsibility to review these terms periodically for any updates or changes.\nBy purchasing and using our services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms and conditions. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us before making a purchase.\n\n\nDo not allow children or other unauthorized family members or friends to access your credit cards or your account at the payment site to ensure that no one pays for a Membership without your permission. By making a payment for Membership to our site, you acknowledge that you have read and agree to the above No Refund and no cancellation Policy.\n\nWe do not offer refunds on subscriptions that have already been taken. The movements in stock market are not always predictable and therefore, Make sure you have gone through the disclaimer, terms and conditions and refund policy before proceeding for subscription or making payment for any of our services.\n\nAll sales are final. Because FINBYTECH IT SOLUTIONS offers a Expert Advice evaluation to ensure that our products and services will meet your needs without the need to purchase, there will be ABSOLUTELY NO REFUNDS and CANCELLATIONS. \n\nBefore deciding to subscribe to our services, please make sure to take our Expert Advice, the evaluation version that we provide. We do not offer refunds on subscriptions that have already been taken. We so believe in our services and support. \n\nFor this reason, we strongly recommend that before payment, our visitors:- \n\nFor this reason, we strongly recommend that before payment, our visitors:- \n\nRead all information about our products, services and support given to our clients. \nEvaluate the quality of our services by taking our Expert Advice. \nRead all About Us and our technical Team. \nRead our Terms of Use. \nRead our Privacy Policy. \n\nTerms and Conditions: \n\nPlease read these terms and conditions carefully before purchasing and using our services. By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please refrain from using our services. \n\n\n1. Non-Refundable Services: \nAll our services, including the purchase of our software, are non-refundable. Once the purchase is made, it is considered final and non-cancellable. We do not provide refunds, in part or in full, for any reason, including but not limited to dissatisfaction with the software, inability to achieve desired results, or financial losses incurred while using our services. \n\n\n2. Evaluation and Research: \nWe highly recommend that you thoroughly evaluate our services, including reading our documentation, reviews, and any available trial versions before making a purchase. It is your responsibility to ensure that our software aligns with your requirements and meets your expectations. We do not guarantee specific outcomes, profitability, or suitability of our services for your specific investment goals or trading strategies. \n\n\n3. Use of Software: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE \nUpon purchasing our software, you are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the software for your personal or business purposes, subject to the terms and conditions outlined herein. You may not distribute, modify, reverse engineer, or resell the software without prior written consent from us. \n\n\n4. Risk Disclosure: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE \nTrading and investing in financial markets carry inherent risks, including the potential for substantial financial losses. We do not provide any guarantee or assurance of profitability or specific investment returns through the use of our software. It is essential that you understand the risks involved and carefully consider your financial situation and risk tolerance before using our services. \n\n\n5. Indemnification: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWAREBy using our services, you agree to indemnify and hold us harmless from any claims, losses, damages, liabilities, and expenses arising from your use of the software or any violation of these terms and conditions. \n\n\n6. Intellectual Property: \nAll intellectual property rights, including copyrights and trademarks, associated with our services, software, documentation, and any related materials, belong to us or our licensors. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any of our intellectual property without obtaining prior written consent from us. \n\n\n7. Limitation of Liability: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE \nIn no event shall we be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to the use of our services, including but not limited to financial losses, business interruption, or loss of data. \n\n\n8. Modification of Terms: FOR API BRIDGE SOFTWARE \nWe reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website. It is your responsibility to review these terms periodically for any updates or changes. \nBy purchasing and using our services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms and conditions. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us before making a purchase. \n\n\nDo not allow children or other unauthorized family members or friends to access your credit cards or your account at the payment site to ensure that no one pays for a Membership without your permission. By making a payment for Membership to our site, you acknowledge that you have read and agree to the above No Refund and no cancellation Policy. \n\nWe do not offer refunds on subscriptions that have already been taken. The movements in stock market are not always predictable and therefore, Make sure you have gone through the disclaimer, terms and conditions and refund policy before proceeding for subscription or making payment for any of our services. \n"
